<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb 0%, #2575fc 100%);
        color: #333;
        padding: 40px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 30px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        text-align: left;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2575fc, #6a11cb);
        color: white;
        padding: 25px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 26px;
        font-weight: bold;
        border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 25px;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }
      .content p {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .details {
        background: #f4f4f4;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #555;
      }
      .details p {
        margin: 5px 0;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2575fc, #6a11cb);
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
        border-radius: 6px;
        transition: 0.3s;
      }
      .btn:hover {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
      }
      .social-links {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
      .social-links a {
        margin: 0 10px;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #6a11cb;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: 0.3s;
      }
      .social-links a:hover {
        color: #2575fc;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 14px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #777;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        Josim
      </div>

      <div class='content'>
        <p>Hello <strong>{{clientName}}</strong>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for reaching out to us! Your message has been received, and
          we will get back to you shortly.</p>

        <div class='details'>
          <p><strong>Your Details:</strong></p>
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{clientEmail}}</p>
          <p><strong>Message:</strong> {{body}}</p>
        </div>

        <p>We typically respond within 24 hours. If your inquiry is urgent, feel
          free to contact us directly.</p>

        <a href='https://yourwebsite.com' class='btn'>Visit Our Website</a>

        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p><strong>Josim</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class='social-links'>
        <p>Follow us on:</p>
        <a href='https://facebook.com/josim' target='_blank'>Facebook</a>
        |
        <a href='https://linkedin.com/in/josim' target='_blank'>LinkedIn</a>
        |
        <a href='https://instagram.com/josim' target='_blank'>Instagram</a>
        |
        <a href='https://x.com/josim' target='_blank'>X (Twitter)</a>
      </div>

      <div class='footer'>
        <p>Â© {{year}} Josim. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>